info.attribution:
The library image by Kendrick has been cropped.  It is from https://www.flickr.com/photos/shrimphead/2259353414/ and is available under a CC BY-NC-SA 2.0 license.

The scroll border on smaller boards is in the Public Domain and is available at https://publicdomainvectors.org.

The game layout, game board, and game piece designs were done by https://www.reddit.com/user/96LawDawg and are released to the Public Domain.
info.description: Classic strategy game.  Take turns placing black and white pieces on intersection of board.  Player controlling most territory wins.
